Former footballer Gary Mabbutt was left with a 30inch scar following a five hour operation to save his leg .
The ex-Tottenham and England star , was rushed to hospital after waking up at 1 am to find that the leg had gone cold back in 2013 .
He was treated at King 's College Hospital in South East London , undergoing an emergency five-hour operation .
The Spurs legend has spoken for the first time about his condition .